\[\mathbb{P}\left(\max(\left\|n\|\bar{x}\right\|^{2}-d\right|,\left\|n\|\bar{z} \right\|^{2}-d\right|)>2t+2\sqrt{dt}\Big{)}\leqslant 4e^{-t}\,.\]

