\[\mathbb{P}\left(\mathcal{A}\right) \leqslant 2^{n}n^{n}e^{-\alpha\beta n/2+\alpha n\log(2)}\] \[=e^{\log(c\sqrt{\beta})\alpha n+n\log(n)+(1+\alpha)n\log(2)}\,.\]

