\[-\log\left(12C\delta^{-1}\log(n)\sigma\right)\geqslant\frac{12(1+\varepsilon) \log(n)}{\delta}=\log\left(n^{\frac{12(1+\varepsilon)}{\delta}}\right)\,,\]

